      </span>
    </a>
    <a href='/campaigns' id="campaign-housing" class="campaign">
      <span class="campaign-content">
        <h3>Yes on Proposition 10</h3>
        <p>
          Prop 10 will allow cities and the state to pass strong, universal rent control. Help us build the movement for rent control and social housing for all!
        </p>

        <u>Read&nbsp;more â†’</u>
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="campaigns-addendum">
    Check out the full list of our <a href="/endorsements">2018 Midterm Election Endorsements here</a>! ðŸ—³
  </div>

  <div id='home-news'>
    <%= render 'featured_posts' %>
  </div>

  <div id='home-events'>
    <%= render 'upcoming_events' %>
  </div>
</div>

